data.name: Combo double buffet vouchers for weekend
data.description:
6-course meal includes one shared appetizer, two main dishes and one shared dessert
Choice of appetizers include: crispy calamari with smoked lemon tartar sauce, trio's sliders featuring beef, chicken & salmon sliders or artichoke spinach dip with crab meat & pita chips
Choice of any two main dishes include: striploin steak featuring smashed potatoes and seasonal vegetables; cornish hen featuring garlic mash, baby carrots and rosemary jus; or salmon with quinoa salad and citrus beurre blanc
Finish the meal with 1 shared dessert, with choice of creme brulee, cheesecake or chocolate cake
Includes wine or beer with your meal and Char 631 Modern Steakhouse offers a wide range of vintage wines and creative cocktails to further enhance your dining experience

data.name: Slim fit long sleeve T Shirt men trend casual
data.description:
Linen T-shirt with thin stripes. Model with round neck and short sleeves MODEL HEIGHT: 189 CM SIZE L. A 100% cotton t-shirt with a professionally applied print, celebrating the incredible Whyman family! Designed and printed just for you by your friends at the Ann Arbor T-shirt Company in Ann Arbor, Michigan. It says: Whyman: English. Attractive, charming, strong, kind, intelligent, and modest. Respected by elders, beloved by children, and admired by peers. The colour-contrasting cuffs on sleeves and neck turn this T-shirt into a sporty companion that can be combined with a host of styles. Relaxed and comfy, high round neck
Sleeve cuffs and neck in contrasting colour. High-quality, pre-shrunk single jersey fabric 175 g/m². Material: 100% cotton
